Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.28,0:04:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我得和雷蒙德見面  一對一\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I want to meet with Raymond, one on one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.93,0:04:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我代表你去談吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Let me speak on your behalf.
