Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.97,0:06:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能是我的手機\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I think it's mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.77,0:07:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,賽斯  現在可是凌晨四點\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Seth, it's four in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.20,0:07:08.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時候\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}When?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.45,0:07:09.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你跟她一起去\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I want you to go with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.67,0:07:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我這就去徵求洛克蘭的批准    -謝謝\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- I'll get it cleared with Rockland right now. -Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.96,0:07:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,密查姆說飛機30分鐘內就能準備好\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Meechum says the plane will be ready in 30 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.43,0:07:18.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,行  很好\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Okay, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.17,0:07:20.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得只是恐慌症發作\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You think it was just a panic attack
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.37,0:07:22.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-還是她真打算...    -我不知道\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- or was she really trying -- -I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.08,0:07:24.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們要她留院觀察一整夜就夠糟了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It was bad enough they felt they had to keep her overnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.61,0:07:26.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我給白宮醫生辦公室打個電話\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm gonna call the White House physician's office,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.49,0:07:28.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-看看他們能不能推薦什麼人 -好\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- see if they can recommend anyone.   - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.06,0:07:30.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-等等  我的手機    -在你手裡\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- Oh, wait. My phone.   - It's in your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.26,0:07:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我今晚回來\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'll be back sometime tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.54,0:07:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,彈劾是我們唯一的機會\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Impeachment is our only chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.05,0:07:43.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這些席位在中期選舉中仍處於爭奪狀態\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Here are the seats that are still in contention in the midterms.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.03,0:07:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這13個我們再怎麼努力也會失去\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}These 13 we're gonna lose no matter what we do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.02,0:07:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但即便我們拿下剩下所有席位\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But even if we win all the rest,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.99,0:07:50.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們也只有五個席位的優勢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}that only leaves us with a five-seat majority.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.67,0:07:52.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要麼保黨  要麼保總統\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We either save the party or we save the president.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.67,0:07:55.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,任何人反對彈劾的人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Anyone who votes against impeachment
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.32,0:07:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在選舉前都會受到攻擊性廣告的攻擊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}is gonna get pommeled by attack ads between now and election day.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.55,0:08:00.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你已經有多少席位了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}How many do you have already?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.09,0:08:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們需要18席  我只有六席\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We need 18. I have six.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.75,0:08:05.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那還要爭取12席\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}So, 12 more to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.03,0:08:10.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唐納德  我知道這是個很大的人情\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Look, Donald, I know this is a big ask
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.28,0:08:12.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你更想把注意力放在政策上  不...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and you prefer to focus on policy and not --
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.47,0:08:16.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傑姬  不用說了  我加入\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Jackie, you can stop. I'm on board.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.28,0:08:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-真的嗎      - 百分百\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- Really?   - 100%.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.25,0:08:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不得不說  我有點驚訝\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I have to say I'm a little surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.70,0:08:24.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你把那些手推車推進休息室的時候  你說\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}When you rolled those dollies into the cloakroom you said,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.49,0:08:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"跟我合作  我不是弗蘭克·安德伍德"\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}"Work with me. I'm not Frank Underwood."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.75,0:08:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後你幫我通過了經濟刺激方案\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And then you helped get my stimulus package through,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.58,0:08:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你信守了諾言\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}just like you promised.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.19,0:08:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次你有什麼期望呢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And what do you expect this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.52,0:08:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你永遠不會成為弗蘭克·安德伍德\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That you never become Frank Underwood.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.87,0:08:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要知道  如果我們成功了  他會取代沃克\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You must realize if we're successful, he will replace Walker.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.75,0:08:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不喜歡弗蘭克  但我更討厭成為少數黨\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I don't like Frank. but I hate being in the minority even more.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.66,0:08:51.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們不能讓共和黨同時執掌國會兩院\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We can't let the Republicans control both houses of Congress.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.78,0:08:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我加入領導層以來  你變了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You've changed since I joined the leadership.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.10,0:08:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是更懂得如何玩這場遊戲了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Just getting better at playing the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.98,0:09:01.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來頑固不化這詞不太對\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I guess you can teach an old liberal new tricks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.77,0:09:04.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來是的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.21,0:09:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我你還需要誰\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}So, tell me who you still need.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.84,0:09:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的律師說我贏得庭審的概率是一半一半\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}My lawyers are saying 50/50 that I survive a trial.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.87,0:09:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不太滿意這個數字\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Now, I'm not a big fan of those odds,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.81,0:09:17.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我願意接受\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}but I'm willing to take 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.45,0:09:19.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你的律師說這事就看運氣\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If your lawyers are putting it at a coin toss,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.55,0:09:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你是花錢僱了一群太過樂觀的人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}then you're paying them too much to be overly optimistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.29,0:09:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼能信任加勒特\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And how can I trust Garrett?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.60,0:09:25.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他背叛了20年的友誼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He turned his back on 20 years of friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.77,0:09:27.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他也可以這麼說你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He could accuse you of the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.96,0:09:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這地球上沒有人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, nobody on this planet
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.50,0:09:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比我更想看弗蘭克·安德伍德進監獄了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}wants to see Frank Underwood go to jail more than I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.13,0:09:38.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是不想到時跟他關在一起\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I just don't want to be sharing a cell with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.58,0:09:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種事不會發生的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That won't happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.67,0:09:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你只給了我加勒特的口頭承諾\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}All you've given me to go on is Garrett's word.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.94,0:09:46.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他想讓你說出實情\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He's asking you to tell the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.32,0:09:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做正確的事的人必有好報\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Good things happen to those who do the right thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.77,0:09:54.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們就指望弗蘭克會跪地求饒\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And you just expect Frank to lie down,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.47,0:09:55.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舉旗認輸嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}throw in the towel, hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.85,0:09:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連求饒的機會也不會給他\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We don't even give him the chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.85,0:09:59.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的證詞會讓他全無反擊之力\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Your testimony knocks him out cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.75,0:10:01.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請稍等\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.67,0:10:09.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事  啊  多謝你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yes? Oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.08,0:10:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請等一下\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.00,0:10:14.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}There you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.15,0:10:22.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑體簡體\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}普契尼歌劇  蝴蝶夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.06,0:10:30.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我妻子送的小禮物\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Care package from my wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.63,0:10:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  請繼續\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Now, you were saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.25,0:10:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我得提醒你一下  她現在狀態很不穩定\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I just want to warn you, she's not herself right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.25,0:10:46.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們不得不給她服用了大劑量的藥物\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}They had to put her on some heavy doses.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.68,0:10:47.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼藥\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Of what?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.86,0:10:50.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主要是碳酸鋰{\fs14}[抗躁狂藥]\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Lithium, mostly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.12,0:10:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不然就得留院觀察30天了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It was either that or commit her for 30 days.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.05,0:10:55.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她現在剛吃了藥  可能有點\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Now she just took some, so she might be a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.03,0:11:05.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅根\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Megan?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.40,0:11:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別碰我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.52,0:11:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你母親告訴我他們從湖裡救起了你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Your mom told me they found you in the lake.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.64,0:11:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有什麼好關心的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What do you care?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.57,0:11:50.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我當然很關心你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I care very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.11,0:11:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才怪\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No, you don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.24,0:11:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒人會利用關心的人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You don't use somebody you care about.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.69,0:12:06.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,娼妓\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Whore.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.95,0:12:09.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蕩婦\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Slut.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.59,0:12:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,婊子\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.02,0:12:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叛徒\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Traitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.89,0:12:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們就是這麼說我的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That's what they call me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.32,0:12:21.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發郵件  在網上\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}In my mail. Online.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.18,0:12:25.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真希望我沒打那通電話\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I wish I'd never called.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.08,0:12:27.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真希望我沒見過你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I wish I'd never met you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.93,0:12:32.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼我信什麼  真是蠢透了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I feel so stupid believing what you told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.48,0:12:34.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為你真心關心我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Thinking that you did care.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.47,0:12:37.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我本來都快恢復了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I was getting better.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.61,0:12:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這全怨你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You did this to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.95,0:12:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我每吃一片藥  都會想到他\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Every time I take one of these I think of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.47,0:12:50.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下來我想到的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And the next face I think of?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.44,0:12:52.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.36,0:13:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得被利用了  我很遺憾\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry that you felt used.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.63,0:13:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有利用你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You weren't.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.74,0:13:08.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I just, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.00,0:13:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像我說的  政治風向變了  而且\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}like I told you, the political landscape shifted and --
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.92,0:13:17.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而我們發現\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and we found...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.16,0:13:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅根\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Megan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.29,0:13:42.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.81,0:13:44.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我收到你的簡訊了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I got your text.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.05,0:13:48.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道我不該聯繫你  但我覺得\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I know I shouldn't be reaching out to you, but I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.37,0:13:50.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  沒關係  我很高興你通知了我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No, that doesn't matter. I'm glad you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.22,0:13:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她怎麼樣\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}How is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.71,0:13:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,狀態很不好\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}In bad shape.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.65,0:13:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說實話我很吃驚他們還敢讓她離開醫院\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm surprised they even let her out of the hospital, to be honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.22,0:14:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼我能做的嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Is there anything I can do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.38,0:14:05.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用不用我聯繫她的親人  親自去探望她\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Should I contact her family or go out there myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.59,0:14:08.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們最好不要打擾她了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We should probably leave her alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.60,0:14:10.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還好嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.81,0:14:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事  你呢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm fine. How about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.56,0:14:17.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還撐得住\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Uh, holding up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.55,0:14:22.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和律師商量了一整天\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Spent the whole day talking to lawyers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.71,0:14:25.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這對孩子們太不容易了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's hard on the kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.44,0:14:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們既窘迫又害怕\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}They're embarrassed and frightened.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.89,0:14:31.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我們會熬過去的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But we'll get through it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.39,0:14:35.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我認為你和加勒特的講話很感人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I thought the speech you and Garrett gave was very moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.76,0:14:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,似乎起了點作用\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, it seems to have helped some.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.30,0:14:40.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實我是受你的啟發\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I was inspired by you, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.09,0:14:44.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你敢於在電視上承認墮過胎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}When you admitted to the abortion on TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.24,0:14:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真相往往很有衝擊力\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The truth is a powerful thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.89,0:14:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特莉莎  我想向你道歉\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Tricia, I want to apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.08,0:14:57.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What for?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.80,0:14:59.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的家庭所經歷這些變故\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I feel partly responsible for everything
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.74,0:15:01.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得有一部分責任在我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}your family's going through.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.50,0:15:07.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我建議你們去見諮詢師\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It was my suggestion that you get counseling.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.61,0:15:11.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早知今日  我當初就什麼都不會說了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And had I known then, I never would have said a word.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.47,0:15:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克萊爾  別這麼說  見諮詢師效果很好\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Claire, please. Counseling was a godsend.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.20,0:15:17.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加勒特和我需要幫助\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Garrett and I needed help,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.33,0:15:18.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且也確實起了作用\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and it's made things better.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.71,0:15:20.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我應該感謝你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I should be thanking you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.73,0:15:22.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有要感謝你把梅根的事告訴我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And thank you for letting me know about Megan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.49,0:15:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你能去看她  真是好心\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It was kind of you to make that trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.33,0:15:30.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是個好人  克萊爾  保重\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You're a good person, Claire. Be well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.78,0:17:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我估計你是想說聽證會的事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I take it this is about my hearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.47,0:17:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是沃克聯繫過你了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Did Walker get to you first?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.72,0:17:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒比你快多少\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Barely.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.05,0:17:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但有時候  哪怕只快一點也足夠了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But sometimes barely is enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.94,0:17:35.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他肯定提出給你特赦\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm sure he offered you a pardon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.38,0:17:38.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,提供競爭對手給不了的  才是最聰明的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Always better to offer something your competitor can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.54,0:17:42.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我能給你更好的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Oh, but I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.27,0:17:46.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,據我所知  憲法規定的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The last time I read the Constitution,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.31,0:17:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,副總統能給的最有價值的東西也就是...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}the most a vice president could offer was, um,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.95,0:17:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陪陪笑臉  遞遞眼色了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}smile and a wink.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.29,0:17:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想我已經證明我不是一般的副總統\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I think I've proven that I'm not your typical vice president.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.26,0:17:57.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一般或不一般  你都輸了  弗蘭克\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Typical or not, you've lost, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.42,0:18:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還有出路  你沒有\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I have an out. You don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.10,0:18:04.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加勒特撐不過彈劾的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Garrett will not survive impeachment.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.21,0:18:07.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你絕不能否認\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If there's one skill you can't deny,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.59,0:18:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我拉選票的能力\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}it's my ability to whip votes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.93,0:18:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是在眾議院  不是在參議院\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}In the House. Not in the Senate.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.05,0:18:16.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但依據憲法  我是參議院的主席\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Which the Constitution makes me the President of.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.23,0:18:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也看到我是怎麼通過福利改革了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And you saw what I did with entitlement.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.00,0:18:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傲慢使你自以為了不起了  弗蘭克\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Hubris is giving you delusions of grandeur, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.27,0:18:26.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算沃克僥倖逃過一劫\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Let's say Walker squeaks by.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.84,0:18:28.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的  你能得到特赦\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yes, you get your pardon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.65,0:18:30.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你把自己跟一個\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But you've bound yourself at the hip
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.65,0:18:33.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有任何政治資本的人拴在一起了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}to a man who has zero political capital.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.07,0:18:40.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果他被定罪  我們都要坐牢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And if he gets convicted, we all go to jail.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.40,0:18:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰都沒有特赦了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}There's no pardon for anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.78,0:18:44.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我願意賭一把\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'll roll the dice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.43,0:18:51.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷蒙德  用你的商業頭腦想想\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Raymond, think like a businessman.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.84,0:18:55.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不就是靠儘量減小風險積累財富的嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Haven't you built a fortune by minimizing risk?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.85,0:18:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不就是你這些年用錢堆砌國會\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Isn't that why you stacked Congress all these years,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.79,0:19:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,引領加勒特當上總統\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}why you guided Garrett to the Oval,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.42,0:19:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,留我當黨鞭的原因嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and why you kept me on as Whip?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.68,0:19:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沃克是個垃圾股  貶值得快\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Walker is a junk bond quickly depreciating,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.45,0:19:10.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而我可以迅速解決和中國的貿易戰\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}whereas I can end the conflict with China
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.02,0:19:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還能保你穩賺\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and keep you in the black.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.10,0:19:15.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你沒法保證改善和中國的關係\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You can't promise better relations with China.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.71,0:19:18.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我破壞的  我也能修復\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I wrecked them. I can repair them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.66,0:19:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一起合作吧  就如我們起初打算的那樣\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Now let's work together, as we always intended to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.02,0:19:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等你被關進棺材大的牢房裡\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}When they put you in that box barely bigger than a coffin,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.01,0:19:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,記住今晚這美妙的音樂吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}remember how beautiful the music was tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.23,0:19:52.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或許能讓你稍微好受點\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It might give you some small degree of comfort.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.47,0:20:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,普契尼太傷感  我喜歡積極向上的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Puccini's a downer. I prefer something much more optimistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.64,0:20:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們不肯放布朗  審判日期已經定了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}They won't touch Brown. The trial date is set.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.50,0:20:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們可以減輕指控\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}They can reduce the charges.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.33,0:20:17.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,達拉斯不願讓步  如果我繼續施壓\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Dallas won't give. If I keep pressing,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.88,0:20:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會顯得可疑\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}it'll start to look suspect.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.03,0:20:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我能確保你不被起訴\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What I can do is make sure you don't get prosecuted.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.05,0:20:25.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有我不再替你工作\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And I stop working for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.67,0:20:27.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不全是  我跟檢察官說\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Not quite. I told the U.S. Attorney
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.73,0:20:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們想讓你為我們工作\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}that we wanted to bring you on with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.44,0:20:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,網路恐怖主義分局  你的案底將一筆勾銷\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Cyber terrorism division. You'd get a clean slate, as --
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.19,0:20:34.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,門都沒有\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No fucking way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.79,0:20:36.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們不會就那麼放棄你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}They're not gonna let your case go
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.36,0:20:38.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除非我們給他們充分的理由\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}unless we give them a compelling reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.31,0:20:40.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-沒別的    -我跟調查局鬥爭了半輩子\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- There's no o   - I've spent half my life fighting the Bureau.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.72,0:20:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只能這麼說\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's the only way I could sell it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.96,0:20:45.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抓住機會  嘉文\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Take this opportunity, Gavin,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.29,0:20:47.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趁他們還沒改變主意\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}before they change their minds.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.36,0:20:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要見道格拉斯·斯坦普\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I want to meet with Douglas Stamper.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.69,0:20:53.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行  我們說好了我幫你找出路\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No. The deal was I find you a way out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.75,0:20:56.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說好的是你幫布朗脫身並且還我自由\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No, the deal was you help out Brown and you give me my freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.31,0:20:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你沒為布朗辦成任何事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You haven't done shit for Brown,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.48,0:20:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還想繼續控制我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and you still want to keep me under your thumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.02,0:21:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我見斯坦普  否則一切免談\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}So I meet Stamper, or any kinda deal is off.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.79,0:21:18.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷蒙德沒答應\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Raymond said no.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.04,0:21:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他沒表態\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He said neither yes nor no.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.36,0:21:21.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會繼續施壓\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'll keep the pressure on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.85,0:21:23.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他還是有可能指證你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}So he could still name you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.85,0:21:25.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的  一切皆有可能\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He could. Anything's possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.68,0:21:26.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你得阻止他\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, you have to stop him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.84,0:21:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在嘗試\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm trying.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.09,0:21:29.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘗試遠遠不夠  弗蘭西斯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, trying's not enough, Francis.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.71,0:21:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我總不能在聽證會上坐他旁邊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, I can't sit next to him in the hearing room
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.51,0:21:32.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿槍抵著他頭\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}with a gun to his head.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.83,0:21:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這聽起來像在找藉口\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Now that sounds like an excuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.35,0:21:35.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事實就是這樣\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's a reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.64,0:21:38.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你答應過  我不用做最壞的打算\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You promised me I wasn't going to have to prepare for the worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.67,0:21:40.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也準備信守諾言\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And I intend to keep that promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.16,0:21:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想確保  我們都要確定會沒事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, I want to be sure. I want both of us to be sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.05,0:21:46.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唯一萬無一失的辦法  就是讓沃克阻止他\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The only surefire way is for Walker to call him off personally.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.42,0:21:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就去辦\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Then make that happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.00,0:21:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不能逼一個拿我當敵人的人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I cannot force a man who thinks I'm his enemy
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.35,0:21:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,突然把我當朋友\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}to suddenly call me his friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.78,0:21:55.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我該做的都做了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I've done what I had to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.25,0:21:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在輪到你了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Now you do what you have to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.42,0:22:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,勾引他  把你的心交給他\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Seduce him. Give him your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.94,0:22:05.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,挖出來放在他手上\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Cut it out and put it in his fucking hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.37,0:23:16.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,親愛的總統先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Dear Mr. President,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.94,0:23:20.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我正在用我離開桑蒂諾時\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm writing on an Underwood portable
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.24,0:23:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我父親給我的安德伍德打字機給你寫信\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}my father gave me when I left for the Sentinel.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.12,0:23:25.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我父親將它給我時說了些話\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It was the words my father said when he gave it to me
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.54,0:23:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑體簡體\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}安德伍德國際
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.96,0:23:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比這臺七十多年的機器更讓我能產生共鳴\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}that have resonated even more than this 70-year-old machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.12,0:23:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"這個安德伍德建立起了一個商業帝國"他說\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}"This Underwood built an empire," He said.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.41,0:23:37.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"現在該你去建立一個屬於你自己的帝國了"\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}"Now you go and build one of your own."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.06,0:23:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這些話一直激勵著我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Those words have been a large part of what has motivated my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.38,0:23:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只用這個打字機寫過另一封信\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I've only written one other letter with these keys.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.12,0:23:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那封信不辱使命  希望這次也一樣\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It did not fail me then. I hope it will not fail me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.08,0:23:57.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說我想削弱你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You said I wanted to diminish you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.28,0:23:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,實際上  我沒有\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The truth is, I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.24,0:24:02.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說我想在2016年跟你競爭\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You said I wanted to challenge you in 2016.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.13,0:24:03.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,實際上  我沒有\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The truth is, I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.08,0:24:06.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說我想自己當總統\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You said I wanted the presidency for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.69,0:24:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,實際上\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The truth is,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.82,0:24:10.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的確想\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.46,0:24:14.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪個政客沒想過\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What politician hasn't dreamed about what it would be like
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.65,0:24:16.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑體簡體\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}戴維營
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.76,0:24:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,宣誓執掌國家最高權力\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}to take the oath of the highest office of our land?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.79,0:24:22.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我曾盯著你的總統辦公桌看  覬覦它\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I've stared at your desk in the Oval and coveted it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.17,0:24:24.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,權力  威望\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The power, the prestige.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.39,0:24:27.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些東西對我這樣一個來自南卡羅來納州\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Those things have a strong pull on someone like me,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.94,0:24:32.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一座小鎮  曾一無所有的人來說有致命的吸引力\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}who came from a small South Carolina town with nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.73,0:24:35.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但自你就職時起\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But since you assumed office,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.31,0:24:37.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我唯一的目標就是為你而戰\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}my only aim has been to fight for you
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.89,0:24:40.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,與你並肩作戰\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and alongside you,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.06,0:24:42.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無論是在國會還是現在\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}whether that be in Congress or as now,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.57,0:24:44.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這場彈劾之戰中\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}the battle over impeachment.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.15,0:24:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或許有一天  我有幸能成為總統\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Maybe one day I'll have my chance to serve as president,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.20,0:24:52.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但絕不是你在任期間\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}but not while you are the nation's leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.80,0:24:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在你身上  我看到了勇敢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And in you, sir, I see a brave man.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.93,0:25:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看到了正直  你是我願意永遠追隨的總統\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}A just man. A president whom I would follow anywhere,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.17,0:25:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無論我們遇到多大的阻力\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}no matter how strong the wind blows against us.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.24,0:25:13.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一件事我從沒對任何人說過\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I want to tell you something I have never told anyone:
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.64,0:25:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我13歲那年在穀倉裡撞見我父親\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}When I was 13 I walked in on my father in the barn.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.67,0:25:19.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他把獵槍伸到嘴裡\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}There was a shotgun in his mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.37,0:25:23.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他朝我擺了擺手說道"過來  弗蘭西斯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He waved me over. "Come here, Francis," He said.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.08,0:25:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,替我扣動扳機"\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}"Pull the trigger for me."
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.38,0:25:29.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為他沒有勇氣自己做\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Because he didn't have the courage to do it himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.33,0:25:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說"不  爸爸"  就離開了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I said, "No, Papa," And walked out,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.75,0:25:33.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道他永遠沒有那個勇氣\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}knowing he would never find that courage.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.71,0:25:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下來的七年裡  我父親生不如死\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The next seven years were hell for my father,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.20,0:25:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我母親和我更加痛苦\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}but even more hell for my mother and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.13,0:25:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他令我們都苦不堪言\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He made all of us miserable.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.22,0:25:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,酗酒  絕望  暴力\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Drinking, despair, violence.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.42,0:25:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一生中唯一的後悔  就是當時沒扣動扳機\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}My only regret in life is that I didn't pull that trigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.55,0:25:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死亡對他來說會是種解脫\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He would have been better off in the grave,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.09,0:25:53.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有他我們也會過得更好\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and we would have been better off without him.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.07,0:25:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不會讓你陷入同樣的境地\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm not going to put you in the same position
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.03,0:25:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像我父親對我那樣\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}as my father put me in.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.65,0:26:02.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,信中附上了一張紙\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You will find enclosed on a separate sheet
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.02,0:26:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上面供認了所有你被指控的罪名\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}a confession to the crimes you have been accused of.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.59,0:26:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都是假的  但我的簽名會使它們成真\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}They're false words, but my signature will make them true.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.91,0:26:11.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有必要的話就用吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Use them if you must.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.54,0:26:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你真的認為我的所作所為都是為了自己\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If you truly believe that I have only served myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.19,0:26:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我已經永遠失去了你的信任\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}then I have forever lost your trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.97,0:26:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我現能做的  只有獻出自己的自由以保住你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}All I can do now is give you my freedom to save your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.72,0:26:28.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說過我會替你承擔責任\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I said I would take the fall for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.06,0:26:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在我把方法告訴你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and now I give you the means to make that happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.91,0:26:34.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要自己扣動扳機\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I am pulling the trigger myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.20,0:26:38.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了實現夢想我們都要做出犧牲\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We all must make sacrifices to achieve our dream,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.59,0:26:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但有時為了大局必須犧牲自己\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}but sometimes we must sacrifice ourselves for the greater good.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.51,0:26:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做出這樣的犧牲是我的榮幸\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It is my honor to make such a sacrifice now.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.19,0:26:49.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你忠實的朋友  至少我仍這樣認為\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Your loyal friend, still in my heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.09,0:26:52.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即便你不這麼想  弗蘭西斯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}if not in yours, Francis.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.19,0:27:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,憲法列出了一般原則\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The Constitution sets forth the general principles --
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.78,0:27:05.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先生  總統的電話\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Sir? The president's on the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.98,0:27:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總統先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.89,0:27:26.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我收到信了  我讓特莉莎也看了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I got your letter. I had Tricia read it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.02,0:27:33.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很糾結  弗蘭克  一半認為你是懇誠的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm torn, Frank. Half of me wants to think you're genuine.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.70,0:27:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,另一半卻一個字也不信\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The other half doesn't trust a word of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.66,0:27:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特莉莎也這麼想嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Does Tricia feel the same way?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.40,0:27:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她信任克萊爾  所以她也想相信你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}She believes in Claire, which inclines her to believe in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.54,0:27:44.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我字字發自肺腑\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I meant every syllable.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.99,0:27:47.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想讓你百分之百地相信\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I wanted you to know beyond a shadow of a doubt
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.68,0:27:50.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我願做任何該做的事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}that I am willing to do whatever is necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.44,0:27:52.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  我為什麼拋不開疑慮呢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, then why can't I shake the shadow?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.36,0:27:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我是個騙子  先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Because I'm a liar, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.49,0:27:59.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我無所顧忌  甚至可以說沒有同情心\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Because I lack scruples and some would even say compassion.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.51,0:28:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但那只是我展示給世人的一面\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But that's just the image that I present to the world
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.05,0:28:05.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為那能使人害怕  讓人尊敬我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}because it elicits fear and respect.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.97,0:28:08.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我不是那樣的人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But it is not who I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.67,0:28:12.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我希望我的信能向你證明這一點\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}My hope was that my letter would prove that to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.44,0:28:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  就算你說的都是真的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, even if you are being genuine,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.13,0:28:19.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對我也沒什麼用\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}that doesn't do much for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.96,0:28:21.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想躲過彈劾\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I won't survive impeachment
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.44,0:28:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能只靠我和我的副總統關繫好\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}because I got along with my vice president.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.02,0:28:27.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  我同意  你需要的不只是我的好意\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No, I agree you need more than my good intentions.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.50,0:28:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,證明給我看  弗蘭克\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Proof. That's what I want to see, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.39,0:28:36.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別光承擔責任  我要結果\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And not just falling on the sword. Show me results.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.46,0:28:39.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那樣我會重新考慮你是否值得信任\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And then I'll reconsider whether you're worth any of my trust at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.64,0:28:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是說投票\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You're talking votes.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.81,0:28:44.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的  拉票是你的強項\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yeah. Whipping votes was your strong suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.15,0:28:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想看到你那一面\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That's the side of you I want to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.36,0:28:48.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經開始著手了  先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I've already begun, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.23,0:28:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  得到票數了嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yeah? You have a count?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.60,0:28:52.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有個大概  形勢一直在變化\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}An approximation. The sands keep shifting.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.19,0:28:54.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們能得到眾議院的支援嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, can we survive the House or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.06,0:28:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有可能  但是傑姬·夏普在阻撓\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Possibly, but Jackie Sharp is making it very difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.75,0:28:58.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我票數\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Give me numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.05,0:28:59.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她需要得到超過18人的支援\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Over half of the 18 that she needs,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.82,0:29:02.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我想從參議院下手\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}which is why I'd like to start focusing on the Senate.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.83,0:29:04.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不覺得現在行動有點早嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Don't you think that's premature?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.45,0:29:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們必須有所準備\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We should be prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.16,0:29:09.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重中之重就是確保你不被定罪\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The key battle is making sure that you avoid conviction.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.60,0:29:14.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你繼續拉票  有訊息告訴我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, you keep whipping, you keep getting me information,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.01,0:29:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就等你電話了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'll answer your calls.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.30,0:29:20.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但別以為你我就此相安無事了  弗蘭克\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But don't take that as a sign of reconciliation, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.12,0:29:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會感激收穫  先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'll sing for my supper, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.46,0:29:25.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我不會以為我能不勞而獲\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I don't expect it for free.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.02,0:29:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們明早再商量\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Let's talk again tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.23,0:29:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你  總統先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Thank you, Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.82,0:29:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說你想有選擇餘地\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You said you wanted options.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.33,0:29:35.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但弗蘭克讓我沒得選  他坑了我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Frank didn't leave me options. He fucked me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.13,0:29:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你和塔斯克沆瀣一氣  先把他坑了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You fucked him first when you sided with Tusk.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.40,0:29:39.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但誰管中間過程怎樣\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But who cares what happened each inning?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.42,0:29:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有臨門一腳才算數\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's the final score that counts.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.64,0:29:44.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在他麾下八年  為他跑前跑後\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Eight years I spent busting my ass in this office.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.73,0:29:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來還是躲不過為他賣命\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I can't seem to escape it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.20,0:29:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是幫我們還是不幫\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You gonna help us or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.60,0:29:49.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要知道我有什麼好處\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I need to know what I gain.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.61,0:29:52.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你會得到關照的    -說具體點\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- You'll be taking care of.   - Specifically.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.12,0:29:56.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等到塵埃落定  再看看要怎麼辦吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We'll see what makes sense when all the chips have fallen.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.44,0:29:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你是要我悶頭往懸崖下跳\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}So you just want me to leap off a cliff
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.96,0:29:59.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,指望著運氣好摔不死嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and hope for a soft landing beneath?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.63,0:30:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在誰都不會要你  除了我們\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No one will touch you now. Nobody except us.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.23,0:30:04.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們就是你最好的運氣\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We're as soft as you're gonna get.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.27,0:30:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能在白宮給我一官半職嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}A job at the White House?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.66,0:30:09.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這我說不準\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No promises.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.66,0:30:11.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結果如何取決於你的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Other than something commensurate
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.27,0:30:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,忠誠度和經驗\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}with your loyalty and experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.77,0:30:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我完全可以就此抽身  開始新的生活\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I could just walk away from it all. Start a new life.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.43,0:30:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你抽不了身  你知道你做不到\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No, you can't. You know you can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.32,0:30:22.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,離了國會山  你只會衰萎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You'd wither away anywhere but the Hill.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.02,0:30:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管你怎麼騙自己\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's never been about the money,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.45,0:30:25.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你做這一行不是為了錢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}no matter what you tell yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.12,0:30:28.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跳槽的時候  弗蘭克求我留下\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}When I left, Frank begged me to stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.88,0:30:31.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他說"這是權和錢二選一"\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}"Power versus money," He said.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.93,0:30:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別屈尊加入那些繳富人稅的人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Don't reduce myself to a tax bracket.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.30,0:30:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他說得對  但我不認為他會求你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He was right. And I doubt he begged.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.26,0:30:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他對了一半\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He was half right.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.29,0:30:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要有權力握在手裡  就比錢有魅力\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Power is better than money for as long as it lasts.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.56,0:30:43.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但權力總會滑出手心\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But it never lasts.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.77,0:30:46.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的回答是什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What's your answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.48,0:30:56.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你當了黨鞭之後變得更冷血了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You've gotten colder since you've taken over this job.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.87,0:31:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣辦事容易些\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It makes things easier.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.09,0:31:02.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是對外嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}On the outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.27,0:31:05.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,內外皆是\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And the inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.40,0:31:09.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想你  傑姬\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I miss you, Jackie.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.90,0:31:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你打算合作的話  就告訴我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Tell me if you'll cooperate.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.53,0:31:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你哥哥在議員手下幹得如何\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}How's your brother enjoying working with the congressman?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.75,0:31:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我接個電話\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Oh, excuse me one second.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.71,0:31:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總統先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.26,0:31:29.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要你打給塔斯克  告訴他交易取消\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I want you to call Tusk. Tell him the deal is off.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.73,0:31:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-什麼    -你說得對\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- What?   - You were right.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.67,0:31:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想冒此風險\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I don't want to take the risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.18,0:31:34.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我已經和他談過了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But I already spoke to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.32,0:31:37.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就再和他談談  告訴他特赦沒戲了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, so speak to him again. And tell him there's no pardon.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.70,0:31:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先生  我起初對這策略確實有些懷疑\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Sir, I -- I -- I was skeptical of this strategy at first,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.45,0:31:43.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我們已經選了這條路  就該走到底\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}but now that we've gone down this road, we should stick to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.46,0:31:45.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,琳達  你還想回來做幕僚長嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Linda, do you still want your job back?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.00,0:31:47.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然  先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Of course, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.51,0:31:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就打給他\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Then make the call.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.13,0:31:55.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想先看看眾議院的結果\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'd rather see what happens in the House
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.42,0:31:57.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再決定要不要幫你們\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}before I get involved in any way.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.82,0:32:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但如果你能表現出對總統堅定的支援\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But if you came out vigorously in defense of the President,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.46,0:32:02.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能會讓司法委員會覺得...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}it might convince the Judiciary Committee --
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.12,0:32:03.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說實話  我並不是很想\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}To be honest, I'm not particularly inclined
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.83,0:32:06.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幫沃克的忙\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}to be doing Walker any favors.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.28,0:32:09.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,邁克爾  我知道他撤銷了你的國務卿提名\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Now, Michael, I know he revoked your nomination.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.82,0:32:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他完全沒有為我爭取\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He didn't fight for me at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.16,0:32:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他那時剛剛當選  還沒有足夠的...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, he'd just been elected. He wasn't in a position to --
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.63,0:32:16.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才怪  他明明有這權力\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Wrong. He had a clear mandate.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.19,0:32:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他完全可以支援我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He was in a strong position to defend me.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.81,0:32:20.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說得對\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.48,0:32:24.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我是總統  我不會那麼輕易放棄\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If I had been President I wouldn't have given in so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.22,0:32:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會在那篇文章曝光後堅定支援你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I would've stuck by you after that article came to light.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.67,0:32:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老實說  如果國務卿是你而不是杜蘭特\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}In fact, if you'd been our secretary of state instead of Durant,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.66,0:32:33.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們和中國的關係或許就不會這麼差了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I don't think we'd be in the mess we are with China.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.76,0:32:35.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但事實是  如果換了我  我也不會\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But the truth is, I wouldn't have nominated you
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.39,0:32:37.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,提名你做國務卿\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}for secretary of state in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.08,0:32:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會提名你做財政部長\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I would have nominated you for secretary of treasury.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.34,0:32:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為你在經濟領域的專業知識\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Because your expertise in economics is even better
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.55,0:32:43.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比你的外交知識強得多\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}than your grasp on foreign affairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.27,0:32:47.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我是總統  你就會做財政部長\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No, if I were president, you'd be secretary of treasury.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.79,0:32:50.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你是總統...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If you were president.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.60,0:32:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.00,0:32:55.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不能這樣\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You can't do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.57,0:32:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.33,0:33:03.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是弗蘭克搗的鬼嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Was it Frank?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.41,0:33:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,琳達  聽我說\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Linda, listen to me --
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.01,0:33:14.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.63,0:33:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.46,0:33:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,交易取消了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The deal is off.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.34,0:33:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她說原因了嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Did she say why?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.14,0:33:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有  只說他改主意了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No. Other than he changed his mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.94,0:33:26.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但肯定是因為弗蘭克\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But it must be Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.90,0:33:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們還是按原計划來\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Then we go back to the original plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.62,0:33:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  和以前一樣拒不解釋\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That's right. You plead the Fifth just like you did before.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.02,0:33:32.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是政治手段\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}This is political theater.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.02,0:33:33.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我們可以矇混過關然後關注    -天吶\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- We get past it and focus on the   - Jesus Christ.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.59,0:33:34.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.76,0:33:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷米·丹頓自願去鄧巴那裡作證  就是現在\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Remy Danton is volunteering to testify to Dunbar, right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.15,0:33:40.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他自願的  不是被傳喚的嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He volunteered? He wasn't subpoenaed?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.38,0:33:41.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看起來是的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Looks that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.12,0:33:43.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他要出賣我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He's gonna sell me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.84,0:33:45.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話他也會遭到起訴\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That would open him up to prosecution.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.92,0:33:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除非他受到了保護\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Unless he's being protected.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.58,0:33:55.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,丹頓在哪\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Where's Danton?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.17,0:33:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我給他助理打電話\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'll call his assistant.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.81,0:34:04.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是否促成外資\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Did you or did you not facilitate foreign money
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.73,0:34:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,流入政治行動委員會\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}being funneled into political action committees?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.83,0:34:11.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根據我律師的意見\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}On the advice of my counsel,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.32,0:34:14.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我保留行使第五修正案的權利\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I reserve my right to invoke the Fifth Amendment.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.05,0:34:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馮山德聲稱你不僅是促成了此事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Xander Feng claims you not only facilitated,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.07,0:34:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,更是最初的策劃者\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}you orchestrated the scheme.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.46,0:34:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你如何迴應這項證詞\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Now what is your response to that testimony?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.95,0:34:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根據我律師的意見  我保留我的權利\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}On the advice of my counsel, I reserve my right to --
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.66,0:34:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你今天可以一直保留你的權利  塔斯克先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You can reserve your right all day long, Mr. Tusk.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.10,0:34:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但等你面對陪審團時\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But when you appear in front of a grand jury,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.78,0:34:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我確信司法部門一定會起訴你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}as I'm sure the Justice Department intends,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.66,0:34:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的沉默將使你垮臺\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}your silence will be your downfall.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.70,0:34:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,議員有問題要問嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Does the congressman have a question?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.75,0:34:40.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可以躲著我們  先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You can hide from us all you want, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.92,0:34:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卻躲不過與你平起平坐的陪審團\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You cannot hide from a jury of your peers.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.30,0:34:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-主席先生    -就這樣吧  我說完了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- Mr. Chairman.   - That's it. I'm done.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.97,0:34:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我放棄我剩餘的時間\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I relinquish the remainder of my time.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.48,0:34:51.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下面交給田納西州女議員\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The chair recognizes the congresswoman from Tennessee.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.07,0:34:52.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,12分鐘  女士\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You have 12 minutes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.65,0:34:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塔斯克先生  我們捲入了與中國的貿易戰中\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Mr. Tusk, our nation is currently embroiled in a trade war with China.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.74,0:34:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這嚴重挫傷了我國的經濟\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It has gutted our economy.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.89,0:35:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,使我們的海軍處於險境\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It has placed our navy in harm's way.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.64,0:35:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-而使我們陷入這困境的總統    -他知道\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- The president who put us there has -- He knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.22,0:35:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.69,0:35:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的委託人保留\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}My client reserves the --
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.90,0:35:13.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他知道  你們不就是想知道這個嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He knew. Isn't that what you're all wondering?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.69,0:35:17.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請安靜\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Quiet, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.56,0:35:19.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道什麼  確切一些\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Knew what, exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.81,0:35:24.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一套機制  它在過去10年裡\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}There was a mechanism by which a great many contributions
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.86,0:35:27.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,貢獻了大量的捐助款\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}were made over the last 10 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.36,0:35:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我仍然認為\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The legality of this mechanism is something
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.75,0:35:33.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這套機制並不觸犯法律\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}that I continue to believe is within the boundaries of the law.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.90,0:35:41.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但至於該機制本身  馮山德先生說得對\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But as for the mechanism itself, Mr. Feng is correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.42,0:35:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我策劃的  是我促成的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I orchestrated it. I facilitated it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.30,0:35:46.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總統是知道的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And the president knew about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.53,0:35:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,丹頓剛剛取消了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Danton just canceled.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.97,0:35:51.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去他的吧  我們有塔斯克\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Screw Danton. We've got Tusk.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.04,0:35:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接通司法部長\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Get me the attorney general.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.83,0:36:04.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有這個必要  塔斯克先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That won't be necessary, Mr. Tusk.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.89,0:36:06.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請和我們走一趟\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If you'll come with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.44,0:36:07.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真可惜\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That's a shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.98,0:36:10.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,手銬也是我遺願清單中的一項呢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Handcuffs were another item on my bucket list.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.79,0:36:13.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這邊走  先生  你有權保持沉默\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Right this way, sir. You have the right to remain silent.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.41,0:36:15.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你所說的一切將用來作為控告你的證據\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Anything you say can and will be used against you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.64,0:36:19.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們談談條件吧  他在聽證會上很配合\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We'll want a bond. For his cooperation in the hearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.27,0:36:21.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,認罪了再談條件\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'll talk bonds if you'll talk a plea.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.24,0:36:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人們對證詞的反應又快又強烈\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Response to the testimony has been swift and vocal.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.45,0:36:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑體簡體\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}白宮觀察  華盛頓爆發抗議  總統沃克未表態
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.33,0:36:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抗議者從昨天起\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Protesters have been gathering in front of
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.02,0:36:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,便聚集在白宮前\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}the White House since yesterday,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.84,0:36:31.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要求總統沃克下臺\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}demanding President Walker's resignation.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.37,0:36:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一份網上請願書在過去24小時裡\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And an online petition has already accumulated
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.86,0:36:37.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經獲得二十多萬人簽名\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}over 200,000 signatures in the past 24 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.71,0:36:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑體簡體\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}梅傑·加勒特  CBS新聞網首席白宮記者
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.83,0:36:40.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兩院公開譴責總統的人數\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The list of lawmakers publicly condemning the president
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.34,0:36:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,越來越多\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}has grown on both sides of the aisle.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.56,0:36:44.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天下午  中國大使\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And this afternoon the Chinese ambassador
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.27,0:36:46.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也譴責了沃克政府\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}also condemned the Walker administration,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.72,0:36:49.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,指責其瞞著北京與腐敗商人做交易\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}saying China would not negotiate with a president
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.13,0:36:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他說中國不會與這樣的總統進行談判\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}who dealt with corrupt businessmen behind Beijing's back.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.75,0:36:54.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如今  兩國的軍艦\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}This at a time when warships from both countries --
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.96,0:36:57.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,與此同時  總統與第一夫人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Meanwhile the president and first lady remain bunkered
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.32,0:37:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仍在戴維營閉門不出  尚未對華盛頓\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}at Camp David and have offered no public response
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.23,0:37:02.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最新的進展發表公開迴應\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}to the most recent developments in Washington.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.37,0:37:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們請到了《華爾街電訊報》的艾拉·薩伊德\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm here with Ayla Sayyad of the Wall Street Telegraph.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.61,0:37:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑體簡體\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}斯科特·瑟曼  ABC七臺新聞組
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.80,0:37:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑體簡體\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}艾拉·薩伊德  《華爾街電訊報》
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.87,0:37:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾拉  我必須先說\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And Ayla, I have to begin by saying that sources
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.64,0:37:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,據國會知情人士透露\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}on the Hill are telling me
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.30,0:37:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,司法委員會可能完全跳過辯論\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}that the Judiciary Committee may bypass debate all together.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.71,0:37:14.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  委員會還沒有人正式發表這樣的聲明\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Uh, no one on the committee has gone on record about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.16,0:37:15.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但如果不是委員會十分傾向於\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But do you think these rumors would be circulating
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.86,0:37:18.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,建議眾議院啟動彈劾程式\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}if there weren't some sort of strong preference
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.04,0:37:20.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不會有這種傳言了吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}to recommend the Articles of Impeachment to the House?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.22,0:37:22.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我認為幾乎可以肯定彈劾很受支援\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I think it's safe to assume there is strong support.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.86,0:37:24.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看到的每份民調都顯示\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Every poll I've seen shows
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.56,0:37:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很大一部分美國人希望更進一步\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}an overwhelming majority of Americans want this to move forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.97,0:37:29.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得政客們不會無視這一點的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I don't think politicians are going to ignore that.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.17,0:37:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經和我的一些同事聊過了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I've talked to a number of my colleagues already.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.56,0:37:33.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,民主黨這邊有些支持者\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}There's support on my side of the aisle.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.46,0:37:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你有多少    -現在包括我在內有五個\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- Well, how many do you have?   - Five at this point, including me.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.59,0:37:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就一共有60個了  還需要七個\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That would put us at 60. We'd still need seven more.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.52,0:37:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也看了昨晚的民調了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You've seen the overnight polls.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.21,0:37:43.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的支援率都降到個位數了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He's dipped down into the single digits.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.73,0:37:46.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想和我們一起發表公開聲明嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Are you willing to make a public statement with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.14,0:37:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得事到如今\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I think the country could use
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.44,0:37:50.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兩黨合作一下也不是壞事吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}a little bipartisanship right now, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.37,0:37:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得他們在虛張聲勢嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Do you think they're bluffing?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.41,0:37:57.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了動搖參議院那些仍在猶豫的人而耍的花招\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That it's some sort of stunt to sway the undecideds in the Senate?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.28,0:38:00.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,邁克爾·科恩小氣又記仇  先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Michael Kern is bitter and small-minded, sir,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.77,0:38:02.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但如果他們沒獲得足夠的支援\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}but he wouldn't appear publicly with Mendoza
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.68,0:38:04.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他不會和門多薩一同公開表態\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}if they didn't have the numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.22,0:38:06.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以想像眾議院的情況比之前更糟了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, I imagine we're worse off in the House than we were before.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.94,0:38:10.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實我本來和傑姬·夏普聊得還挺有成效\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}In fact, I had a very productive conversation with Jackie Sharp.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.06,0:38:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她同意停止攻擊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}She agreed to stop the attack
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.73,0:38:14.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要我們在中期選舉後支援她做多數黨領袖\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}if we give her our support for majority leader after the midterms.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.36,0:38:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但雷蒙德一提供他的證詞\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But once Raymond gave his testimony,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.55,0:38:18.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她就打電話說交易取消\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}she called to say the deal was off.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.40,0:38:21.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷蒙德真的給了我們很大打擊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Raymond really has set us back.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.28,0:38:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真想不通他為什麼要撒謊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I can't fathom why he lied.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.90,0:38:25.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他要報復我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, it's retribution.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.47,0:38:28.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-為了什麼  能源危機嗎    -不是\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- For what? The energy crisis?   - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.97,0:38:32.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你給了他什麼好處嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Did you offer him something?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.93,0:38:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷蒙德的證詞確實於我們不利\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, Raymond's testimony hurts,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.70,0:38:37.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但並沒有終結我們\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}but it can't finish us off.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.76,0:38:39.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謊言是無法證明的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's impossible to prove a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.83,0:38:41.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,彈劾不可避免\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Impeachment is inevitable.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.47,0:38:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在民眾輿論成了敵人  事實已經不重要了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Public opinion is the adversary now. Facts no longer matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.66,0:38:50.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你應該給科恩打個電話  親自聊聊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You should give Kern a call. The personal touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.24,0:38:51.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果他重新支援我們\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If he came back to us,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.71,0:38:54.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別的民主黨可能就會膽怯退縮\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}it might make the other Democrats get cold feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.03,0:38:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,中國也在幫倒忙\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, China isn't helping.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.13,0:38:58.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,錢主席不回我的電話\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}President Qian won't return my calls.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.06,0:38:59.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,北京那邊肯定覺得我氣數已盡\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Beijing must smell death.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.74,0:39:02.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們只是在利用這個局面尋求籌碼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}They're just exploiting the situation for leverage.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.73,0:39:04.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在暫時別考慮中國\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Let's not worry about China for the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.64,0:39:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一步一步慢慢來  先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}One battle at a time, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.23,0:39:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我大概是完了  弗蘭克\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Maybe I'm finished, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.30,0:39:13.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也許我該接受  我們沒法全身而退了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Maybe I need to start accepting that we won't pull out of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.58,0:39:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總統先生  我知道你累了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Mr. President, I know you're tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.87,0:39:17.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道對你而言  這生不如死\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I know this has been hell for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.61,0:39:20.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,確實  彈劾會是個嚴重的打擊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And, yes, impeachment would be an awful blow.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.44,0:39:23.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們要在參議院浴血奮戰了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We'd have to fight tooth and nail in the Senate.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.44,0:39:25.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,確實  我們將不得不祈求和妥協\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And, yes, we'll have to beg and compromise
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.85,0:39:28.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重新賺回我們的政治資本\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}to regain our political capital.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.05,0:39:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我們一定會勝利  先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But we have it in us, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.30,0:39:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管拼得多麼頭破血流\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No matter how many scars it leaves us with.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.41,0:39:35.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不僅僅是我們  弗蘭克\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's not just us, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.87,0:39:38.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有特莉莎  還有我的孩子們\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's Tricia. It's my children.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.37,0:39:43.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我整夜失眠  想著他們看到父親退縮\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I stay awake at night, thinking how much it would crush them,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.09,0:39:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將是多大的打擊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}seeing their father hauled off.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.30,0:39:48.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先生  不會那樣的  我不會允許\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Sir, that won't happen because I won't let it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.74,0:39:50.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我們遇上最糟的情況\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If we're confronted by the worst,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.16,0:39:52.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我至少會確保你不會遭受牢獄之災\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'll make sure you never step foot behind bars.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.91,0:39:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我向你保證\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You have my word on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.52,0:39:59.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他現在身處黑暗\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He's in the darkness now.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.57,0:40:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是唯一指路的明燈\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And I'm the only beacon of light.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.80,0:40:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在只要溫柔地把他引向礁石就可以了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Now we gently guide him toward the rocks.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.70,0:40:08.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總統先生  你還有我的信\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Mr. President, you also still have my letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.96,0:40:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你想走那條路  現在還不算太晚\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's not too late, if you want to use that option.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.73,0:40:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  你留在國會比待在監獄更有用\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No, you're more useful to me on the Hill than in handcuffs.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.18,0:40:18.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會給科恩打電話\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'll call Kern.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.83,0:40:21.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-晚安  先生    -晚安\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- Goodnight, sir.   - Night.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.27,0:40:52.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,格林告訴你多少\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}How much did Green tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.95,0:40:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,足夠讓我現身\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Enough that I showed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.94,0:40:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他大概沒提到瑞秋·波斯納  是吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He probably didn't mention Rachel Posner, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.26,0:41:01.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心  他不知道\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Don't worry. He doesn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.96,0:41:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我知道\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.63,0:41:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你把她藏在喬帕的一間公寓裡\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You have her in an apartment in Joppa.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.76,0:41:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你的一舉一動\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I have your movements.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.39,0:41:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有你毀掉手機之前的簡訊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I have your text messages before you destroyed your phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.59,0:41:15.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過這已經足夠了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But that's more than enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.00,0:41:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我相信很多人都很想知道她知道的事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'll bet a lot of people would like to know what she knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.50,0:41:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你給我聽好了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Now you listen to me very carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.74,0:41:26.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管你以為你拿到了什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Whatever you think you've got,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.96,0:41:28.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不管你打算拿這些東西做什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}whatever you intend to do with it,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.68,0:41:32.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不會像格林那樣被敲詐牽著走\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I don't respond to extortion the same way that Green does.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.73,0:41:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,格林給你的許諾\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What Green promised you,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.23,0:41:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我瞬間就可以抵消\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}that can be undone in a heartbeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.21,0:41:42.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以才把你找來  確保不會變卦\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And that's why you're here. Make sure it isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.98,0:41:48.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想要我的保護\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You want my protection.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.81,0:41:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不信任格林或聯調局的任何人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I don't trust Green or anyone at the Bureau.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.83,0:41:57.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有誰知道\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Who else knows about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.83,0:42:00.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒人知道\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No one.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.41,0:42:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我為什麼要相信你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Why should I trust you?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.01,0:42:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我們兩人都輸不起  夥計\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}'Cause we both have too much to lose, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.67,0:42:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,穿上衣服\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Get dressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.62,0:42:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What -- what are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.64,0:42:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,穿上衣服\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Put some clothes on.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.73,0:42:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Why -- why?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.24,0:42:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點  我們走\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Now. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.34,0:42:49.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人聯繫你嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Did anyone contact you?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.84,0:42:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要帶我去哪\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Where are you taking me?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.98,0:42:54.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回答我的問題\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Answer my question.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.35,0:42:58.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒人聯繫我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No. Nobody.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.62,0:43:03.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人知道了我們的事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}There's someone who knows about us.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.75,0:43:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道你在哪\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Who knows where you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.63,0:43:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道我們什麼時候見過面\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And when we've met.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.32,0:43:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是要傷害我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Are you gonna hurt me?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.54,0:43:18.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你和我說實話就什麼都不會發生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Nothing's going to happen if you tell the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.25,0:43:21.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在說實話  沒有任何人和我聯繫\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I am. I -- I haven't been contacted by anybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.39,0:43:24.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別再撒謊了  瑞秋\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Stop lying, Rachel.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.76,0:43:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你讓我幹什麼都行\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I will do whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.88,0:43:29.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,求你別傷害我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Please, just don't hurt me.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.85,0:43:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想讓你回答我的問題\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What I want is for you to answer my questions,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.87,0:43:33.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣我才能幫你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}so I can help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.92,0:43:35.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一直以來都在毀掉我的生活\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}All you have ever done is fuck up my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.22,0:43:37.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你毀了團契的事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You fucked up the fellowship.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.13,0:43:38.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你毀了我和麗薩的感情\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You fucked up what I had with Lisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.59,0:43:39.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使我都按你說的做了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Even when I did what you asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.89,0:43:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你每次來找我都像變態一樣\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And your sick fucking visits,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.50,0:43:44.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要我哄小孩似的給你讀書\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and reading to you like a fucking child.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.55,0:43:46.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有什麼毛病\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What is wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.01,0:43:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你就不能放了我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Why can't you just leave me be?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.50,0:43:50.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-為什麼你非要這麼    -住嘴\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- Why do you have to be such a fucking --   - stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.31,0:44:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瑞秋  別做傻事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Rachel? Don't be stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.56,0:44:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瑞秋\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Rachel?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.09,0:44:51.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會有事的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Everything's gonna be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.40,0:45:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我做的一切都是想保護你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}All I've ever done is try to protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.35,0:45:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我現在也是想保護你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That's what I'm trying to do now.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.25,0:45:06.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要相信我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You have to believe that.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.19,0:45:09.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我本來沒必要保護你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I didn't have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.73,0:45:12.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那樣事情會簡單得多\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Been a lot easier if I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.19,0:45:18.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我還是那樣做了  因為我...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But I did. I did it because I --
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.91,0:45:27.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你幹什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.58,0:45:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨天我們結束了關於\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yesterday we completed hearings with regard to Articles
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.10,0:45:55.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,彈劾美國總統的聽證會\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}of Impeachment for the president of the United States.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.11,0:45:57.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主席現在開始聽取委員會動議\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The chair will now entertain motions from the committee.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.03,0:45:59.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主席先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Mr. Chairman.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.09,0:46:01.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主席請阿拉巴馬州議員發言\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The chair recognizes the congressman from Alabama.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.45,0:46:06.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我建議我們直接開始對提議進行投票\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I move that we put our recommendation directly to a vote
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.22,0:46:08.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣眾議院435名成員\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}so that debate on this important matter may take place
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.59,0:46:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都可以就此事進行辯論\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}on the House floor, open to all 435 members.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.33,0:46:16.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,委員會有人反對跳過辯論階段嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Are there any objections to bypassing debate in this committee?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.72,0:46:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在開始對是否將彈劾條款\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We will now vote on recommendation of the Articles
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.83,0:46:23.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,送交眾議院投票進行表決\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}of Impeachment to the full House.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.21,0:46:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,同意提議的請喊"贊成"\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Those in favor of recommendation say, "Aye."
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.80,0:46:27.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,贊成\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Aye.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.08,0:46:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反對者\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Those opposed?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.10,0:46:29.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反對\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Nay.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.66,0:46:31.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,贊成佔多數\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The ayes have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.03,0:46:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,委員會正式建議眾議院\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}This committee officially recommends Articles
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.04,0:46:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對彈劾條款進行投票\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}of Impeachment proceed to the House floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.68,0:46:56.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他來了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.52,0:47:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,副總統剛剛到達戴維營\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The vice president is just arriving now here at Camp David.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.52,0:47:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑體簡體\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}重大新聞  副總統抵達戴維營
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.25,0:47:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們預計沃克總統\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We except President Walker to speak within the hour,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.29,0:47:35.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會在一小時內宣佈\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}announcing his official resignation
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.43,0:47:37.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辭去美國總統的職務\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}as president of the United States.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.72,0:47:54.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你怎麼樣    -我還好\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- How are you?   - I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.25,0:47:58.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總統先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.64,0:48:01.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在廚房裡煮了咖啡\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I have coffee in the kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.95,0:48:03.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-要來點嗎    -不用了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- Would you like some?   - I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.85,0:48:15.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你馬上就要成為\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, you're about to become
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.97,0:48:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自由世界最有權勢的人了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}the most powerful man in the free world.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.47,0:48:20.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你沒必要這麼做  先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You don't have to do this, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:20.97,0:48:22.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我昨晚和科恩談過了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I spoke to Kern last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.03,0:48:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他不肯讓步\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He's not gonna back down.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.52,0:48:26.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我們就打敗他\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}So we'll beat him down.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.05,0:48:27.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  弗蘭克\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.39,0:48:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的支援率只剩8%了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}My approvals are at eight percent.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.48,0:48:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使我不被定罪\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Even if I avoid conviction,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.04,0:48:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也沒有威嚴領導國家了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I have no mandate to lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.94,0:48:36.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我還是有尊嚴地下臺\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}So better I step aside with some dignity
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.32,0:48:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓國家開始康復\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}so the nation can start to heal.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.07,0:48:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我永遠無法與你比肩  先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I can never fill your shoes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.95,0:48:52.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你現在沒有選擇了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You don't have a choice now.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.83,0:49:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的信\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Your letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.15,0:49:13.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.45,0:49:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們去向大家引見美國第46任總統吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}shall we go introduce the 46th president of the United States?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.53,0:49:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑體簡體\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}總統先生收
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.25,0:49:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自即日起\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Effective immediately,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.69,0:49:40.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我辭去美國總統一職\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I am resigning the presidency of the United States.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.53,0:49:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特莉莎和我認為這是最合適的行動\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Tricia and I believe that this is the best course of action,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.98,0:49:47.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既是為了我們和孩子\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}not only for us and our children,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:48.41,0:49:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,更是為了這個國家\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}but for the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:50.53,0:49:53.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這對我們是不幸的一天  毫無疑問\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's a sad day for us. I can't deny that.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.11,0:49:55.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但讓我心有慰藉的是\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But I take solace in this:
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.73,0:50:01.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弗蘭克·安德伍德將把美德  經驗\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Frank Underwood will bring virtue, experience,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.04,0:50:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和勇氣帶入總統辦公室\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and courage to the Oval Office.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.05,0:50:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由他擔任我的副總統  是我的榮幸\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I have been blessed to have him as my vice president.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.19,0:50:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而有他這樣的朋友  更是我的幸運\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But I'm even more blessed to call him my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.98,0:50:14.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能夠擔任\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It has been...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.69,0:50:19.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總統一職  服務國家\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}the greatest honor of my life
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.68,0:50:21.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我這一生無上的榮耀\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}to serve this country as president.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.74,0:50:26.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我感謝我的家人  白宮的工作人員\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I thank my family, my staff,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.01,0:50:28.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以及所有那些支援我的人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and all of those who have supported me.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.40,0:50:31.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,儘管最近幾個月風波不斷\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Despite the last few months,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.41,0:50:35.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我對祖國的信仰愈發堅定\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}my faith in this country has never been stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.20,0:50:37.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上帝保佑你們\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}God bless all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.23,0:50:40.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上帝保佑美利堅合眾國\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And god bless the United States of America.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.81,0:50:45.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你的美言  總統先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Thank you, Mr. President, for those words.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.41,0:50:47.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祝你好運  先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Good luck to you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.07,0:51:04.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先生  請舉起右手  跟我宣誓\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Sir, please raise your right hand and repeat after me.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.01,0:51:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本人  弗蘭西斯·J·安德伍德\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I, Francis J. Underwood...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.76,0:51:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本人  弗蘭西斯·J·安德伍德\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I, Francis J. Underwood...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.27,0:51:11.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在此莊嚴宣誓\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Do solemnly swear...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.67,0:51:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在此莊嚴宣誓\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Do solemnly swear...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:15.83,0:51:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總統先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:17.05,0:51:18.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總統先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.98,0:51:20.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,國務卿女士\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Madam Secretary.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.42,0:51:22.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,內閣其餘成員都在白宮等你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The rest of the Cabinet is awaiting you at the White House.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.94,0:51:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們希望馬上\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We'd like to give you
Dialogue: 0,0:51:24.18,0:51:25.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為你做國家安全簡報  長官\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}a national security briefing right away, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.43,0:51:26.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,細節我都已經清楚了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm aware of the particulars.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:26.43,0:51:28.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請聯繫一下北京\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Can you please get Beijing on the phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.45,0:51:31.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,錢主席已經兩天沒回過總統的電話了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Qian hasn't returned the President's calls for two days.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.46,0:51:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在總統已經換人了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, there's a new president now.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:35.86,0:51:37.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馬上給他打電話\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Please get him on the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:39.55,0:51:41.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兩個小時前  作為三軍統帥\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Two hours ago, President Underwood,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.54,0:51:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安德伍德總統下達了第一條命令\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}in his first act as commander in chief,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.01,0:51:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他要求第七艦隊撤出日本周邊海域\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}gave orders to the seventh fleet to vacate Japanese waters.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:47.41,0:51:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這得益於總統與錢主席進行的一次\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}This was a result of a productive conversation
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.02,0:51:51.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,頗有成效的對話\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}with President Qian,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.22,0:51:52.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而錢主席也對該海域的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}who gave similar orders
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.35,0:51:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,中國艦隊下達了撤退的命令\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}to Chinese naval vessels in the same region.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.91,0:51:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他行動挺快啊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He moves quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:55.75,0:51:57.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是說對中國人  還是對沃克\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Do you mean with the Chinese or with Walker?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.16,0:52:04.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-馮先生    -怎麼了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- Mr. Feng?   - What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.96,0:52:07.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們是司法部的  請隨我們走一趟\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}U.S. Justice Department. We need you to come with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.25,0:52:10.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-去哪    -你將被遣返回中國\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- Where?   - You're going back to China.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.12,0:52:12.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我申請了政治避難\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I have asylum.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:12.43,0:52:15.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  先生  你的避難請求已經被駁回了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No, sir, you don't. Your asylum has been rescinded.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.26,0:52:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有書面證明  無條件無限期的庇護\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I have it in writing. Unconditional and permanent.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.50,0:52:20.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先生  我說過了  對你的庇護已經作廢了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Sir, I'm telling you, your asylum has been rescinded.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.59,0:52:23.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在請收拾個人物品  跟我們走\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Now, please, gather your things and come with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:26.71,0:52:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,撤銷他的避難不是沒有後果的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Revoking his asylum will have consequences.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:29.54,0:52:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是法律上沒問題吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But we're solid from a legal perspective?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:31.38,0:52:35.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,法律上沒問題  他的檔案還沒進入批准流程\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Legally yes. His initial paperwork hasn't been processed,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.22,0:52:38.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們可以聲稱他對我國利益構成威脅\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and we can claim he poses a threat to our national interests.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.54,0:52:41.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但這會削弱國務院的信譽\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But it diminishes the integrity of our State Department.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.23,0:52:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪一個更重要  凱茜  信譽還是和平\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What's more important, Cathy? Integrity or peace?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.33,0:52:48.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道他會被處決的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You know they'll execute him.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.13,0:52:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,中國人說對了一件事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The Chinese are right about one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.10,0:52:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有時候  就得捨棄一人  保證全局\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Sometimes you have to sacrifice the one for the many.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:54.46,0:52:55.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們回華盛頓吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Let's get back to Washington.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.10,0:53:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的  請及時通知我  非常感謝\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Okay. Please let me know. Thanks very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:08.86,0:53:10.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-有訊息嗎    -還是沒有\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- Anything?   - Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.34,0:53:12.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看看能不能通過戒酒互助會查到他的行蹤\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}See if you can track down anyone from his regular AA meetings.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.82,0:53:13.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和輔導員談過了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I spoke to the moderator.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.69,0:53:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他說已經有好幾周沒見過道格了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He said he hasn't seen Doug in several weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:15.90,0:53:18.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我查過醫院  問過他的房東\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I checked all the hospitals, his landlord...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.29,0:53:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先生  人都到齊了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Sir, everyone's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.00,0:53:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好  等手頭事一過\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}All right, when this is all over
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.26,0:53:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要你和南茜一起找道格\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I want you to work with Nancy on finding Doug.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.99,0:53:24.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經和交管部打過招呼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I've already alerted the D.C. Metro.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:24.87,0:53:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們會對他的車牌釋出全境通告\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}They put out an APB on his car.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.12,0:53:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們會找到他的  先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We'll find him, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:27.39,0:53:28.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克萊爾呢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Claire?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:28.15,0:53:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就在外面\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Just outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:29.37,0:53:30.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咱們走  南茜\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Let's go, Nancy.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:40.88,0:53:42.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,女士們先生們\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Ladies and gentleman,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:42.60,0:53:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎總統先生和第一夫人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}the President and the first lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:31.23,0:54:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弗蘭西斯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Francis,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.79,0:54:36.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道離你生日還有段時間\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I know your birthday isn't for a couple weeks,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.62,0:54:37.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我要送你一份禮物\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}but I got you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:37.58,0:54:39.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-這是什麼    -開啟嘛\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- What's this?   - Open it.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.48,0:54:49.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我讓人新做了一個\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I had a new one made.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.54,0:54:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我愛你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.07,0:54:55.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也愛你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I love you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:57.60,0:54:58.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你快進去吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:59.17,0:55:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一起來吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:00.63,0:55:02.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是我們共同的成功\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We earned this together.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.38,0:55:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你先自己去  好好享受一下\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Take a few moments for yourself first.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:05.72,0:55:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就在外面\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'll be out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:51.94,0:57:21.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(193,145)\fad(500,500)}{\3c&HFFFFFF&\fscy1800\fscx3400\c&H000000&\bord1\shad0}■
Dialogue: 0,0:56:51.94,0:57:21.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fad(800,800)\fs18\pos(193,145)\fn方正小標宋_GBK\c&HFFFFFF&\bord0\shad0\b1}1789年4月21日  美國第一任副總統約翰·亞當斯在紐約宣誓就職時\N當選總統喬治·華盛頓還在趕往臨時首都的路上\N直到4月30日才正式就任  所以在30日之前的9天裡\N亞當斯作為副總統就成了這個年輕國家的最高行政長官\N美國是先有有副總統  後有總統的\N美國歷史上  曾有9位副總統因總統亡故或辭職而接任成為總統\N1973年  美國副總統阿格紐因貪腐被調查而被迫辭職\N來自密西根州的眾議員福特被時任總統的尼克森任命為副總統\N次年  尼克森因水門事件被迫辭職  福特成為美國第38任總統\N福特和弗蘭克·安德伍德是美國歷史上\N僅有的兩名未經民主選舉卻擔任過副總統和總統職位的人
